Upon opening any coffin excluding the [[Grand Hallowed Coffin]], there is a 1% chance of a ghostly knight who once served their [[Justiciar]]s to appear. The Grand Hallowed Coffin has a chance for the [[Archpriest of the Unicorn]] to appear instead. After speaking to them (with or without an [[amulet of ghostspeak]]), they will appear in the Hallowed Sepulchre's lobby if players wear a [[ring of visibility]].

